channel.title: Project Prodigy v1
channel.description:
First attempt at a building from a base source, so if you feel flaming helps, go for it. Anyways~
I AM NOT ADVERTISING
Credits: TestScape: 35% Base Source Me: 50% building, coding it. MoparScape TuTs: 15% very helpful.
Working Specials [img]http://img524.imageshack.us/img524/9655/prodigy1aa4.jpg[/img]
[img]http://img220.imageshack.us/img220/336/prodigy5lj2.jpg[/img]
[img]http://img227.imageshack.us/img227/8879/prodigy6fd5.jpg[/img]
Working Prayers: [img]http://img155.imageshack.us/img155/1539/prodigy2hd6.jpg[/img]
Shops, portals: (Also highlighted on mini map) [img]http://img227.imageshack.us/img227/3317/prodigy4km9.jpg[/img]
Money making ways on here: [img]http://img227.imageshack.us/img227/1/prodigy3rs2.jpg[/img]
NOTE: This is TestScape base source, Everything has been moved, fixed; edited by ME. But, of course there is more for me to add, -- ALL skills except agility work at this point. ALL Specials except MAGE SHORT work at this point.
Will be adding a bunch more features, but this isn't a bad start i reckon? First attempt ever anyway :eek:
